  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Evidence"/>
  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Contests Sweepstakes or Games
When we run a contest or sweepstakes or game relating to our Sites it will be accompanied by a set of rules The rules for each contest sweepstakes or game will specify how the information gathered from you for entry will be used and disclosed if it is different than as described in this privacy policy In conjunction with your entry in such contest or sweepstakes personally identifiable information will be collected only if you voluntarily submit it</evidenceContent>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

